2.Create a hyperlink on the web page and this link will switch to other webpage. In second page there is a link as "Back" which will display the first page.
 Ans:
 Home.html:
 <html>
    <head>
        <title>
            Assignment 02 page 01
        </title>
    </head>
    <body>
         <h1>This is Home Page</h1>
        <a href="Ass_02_page02.html">Go to next page !!</a>
    </body>
</html>
Next.html:
<html>
    <head>
        <title>
            Assignment 02 page 02
        </title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>This is Next Page</h1>
        <a href="Ass_02_page01.html">Go back home !!</a>
    </body>
</html>
