3.Create a Paragraph and apply the tags on this paragraph : bold,italic,underline, Mark, strike ,superscript and subscript, emphasis,strong,big.
 Ans:
 <html>
    <head>
        <title>
            Assignment 03
        </title>
    </head>
    <body>
        <p>
            <b>
                This line is Bold.<br>
            </b>
            <i>
                This line is Italic.<br>
            </i>
            <u>
                This line is Underline.<br>
            </u>
            <mark>
                This line is Mark.<br>
            </mark>
            <strike>
                This line is Strike.<br>
            </strike>
            This is superscript and subscript:=<br>
            X<sup>4</sup> is not Equal to X<sub>2</sub><br>
            <em>
                This line is emphasis.<br>
            </em>
            <strong>
                This line is Strong.<br>
            </strong>
            <big>
                This line is Big.<br>
            </big>
        </p>
    </body>
</html>
