7 Create a LoginPage in which background color of textbox should be skyblue. Placeholder should be applied and password length must be atleast 8 characters.
 Ans:
 <html>
    <head>
        <title>Assignment 07</title>
        <style>
            .c1
            {
                background-color: skyblue;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body >
        <form>
			<fieldset>
				<legend><b>Way To Virtua World !!</b></legend>
            Username : <input type="text" class="c1"
						placeholder="Give Your User ID Here"><br><br>
            Password : <input type="password" class="c1"  
					   minlength="8" placeholder="Give Your Pass Word Here" required><br><br> 
            <input type="submit" value="Log_in">
			</fieldset>	
        </form>
    </body>
</html>
