30 Create a confirm box on giving some message.If User clicks Ok button , then background color of the body should be green, If user clicks on cancel button then 
    background color should be red.
 Ans:
 <html>
	<body id="id1">
		<script>
			var con=confirm("Help Poor")
			var headingElement= document.getElementById("id1");
			
			if(con)
				{
					 headingElement.style.backgroundColor="Green";
				}
			else
				{
					 headingElement.style.backgroundColor="red";
				}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
